---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout lang="en" title="FAQ | Agua Sala" description="Frequently asked questions about stay, arrival and bookings.">
  <section class="container-site py-16 md:py-24">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-[--color-brand-700]">FAQ</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 font-serif text-4xl text-stone-900 md:text-5xl">Frequently asked questions</h1>
    <div class="mt-10 space-y-4">
      <details class="rounded-xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-stone-900">What is the maximum capacity?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">The house has capacity for up to 7 guests.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-stone-900">How many bedrooms does it have and how are they distributed?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">
          It has 3 bedrooms: the first with 2 beds of 0.90; the second with 1 bed of 0.90 and
          a double of 1.35; and the third with a double bed of 1.50.
        </p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-stone-900">How can I book?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">You can book via WhatsApp or by sending the inquiry form.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-xl bg-white p-5 ring-1 ring-stone-200">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-stone-900">Who is the house aimed at?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-stone-600">It is ideal for families, groups of friends and international travelers.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>